description: This file defines function prototypes and macros for the Content Filtering Reporting Message Management Object, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: CfRmmoComponentCreate
methods.description: Creates a component instance of the Content Filtering Reporting Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfRmmoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Content Filtering Reporting Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfRmmoRemove
methods.description: Removes an instance of the Content Filtering Reporting Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfRmmoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the Content Filtering Reporting Message Management Object.

methods.name: CfRmmoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Content Filtering Reporting Message Management Object.
